<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="O" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Oerspread" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">O'erspread,</orth> to cover: <cit><quote>the dragon wing of night --s the earth,</quote> <bibl n="shak. tro 5.8.17" default="NO" valid="yes">Troil. V, 8, 17</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>with hostile forces he'll o. the land,</quote> <bibl n="shak. per 1.2.24" default="NO" valid="yes">Per. I, 2, 24</bibl></cit>.
